precis:
Amendment to the SPECIAL DUTY AREA PENSION ORDER which adds a number of
African countries to the schedule of countries designated as "Special
Service Areas" (Angola, Algeria, Morocco, Mauritania/Western Sahara,
Ethiopia and Djibouti).
